Class ArrayListOfLongsWritable

  • java.lang.Object
    • edu.umd.cloud9.util.array.ArrayListOfLongs
      • edu.umd.cloud9.io.array.ArrayListOfLongsWritable
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Cloneable, Comparable<ArrayListOfLongsWritable>, Iterable<Long>, RandomAccess, Writable, WritableComparable<ArrayListOfLongsWritable>

    public class ArrayListOfLongsWritable
extends ArrayListOfLongs
implements WritableComparable<ArrayListOfLongsWritable>
    Writable extension of the ArrayListOfLongs class. This class provides an efficient data structure to store a list of longs for MapReduce jobs.
    Author:
    Jimmy Lin
